---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Travel Grants</h1>

    <p class="mb-4">
      We are pleased to offer travel grants to support attendees who require
      financial assistance to participate in the Hendra@30 conference. These
      grants are intended to help cover travel expenses, such as transportation
      and accommodation.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Eligibility</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
      <li>Applicants must be presenting authors of accepted abstracts.</li>
      <li>
        Priority will be given to early-career researchers, postgraduate
        students, and researchers from low- and middle-income countries.
      </li>
      <li>Applicants must demonstrate financial need.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Application Process</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      To apply for a travel grant, please complete the online application form
      by the specified deadline. The application form will require you to
      provide the following information:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
      <li>Contact information</li>
      <li>Abstract title and author information</li>
      <li>Brief statement of financial need</li>
      <li>Estimated travel expenses</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Successful applicants will be notified via email and provided with further
      instructions on how to claim their travel grant.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Contact Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      For enquiries about travel grants, please contact <a
        href="mailto:info@hendra30.com.au"
        class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">info@hendra30.com.au</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
